reviews.title: Amazing computer for it's age and price
reviews.description: Amazing computer for it's age and price. Very much recommend running snow leopard (second latest it can handle) for its super speed and reliability, despite not being able to install the latest version of things. I have one and it literally runs just as good (after upgrade to 6 gb ram) as my 2013 Samsung Series 5 laptop, even tho I treat it like my baby.
